---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../components/ComparisonTable.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="ISP Proxies"
  description="Compare ISP proxy pricing. Static residential IPs that combine speed and legitimacy."
>
  <div class="container" style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>ISP Proxy Comparison</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        Static residential IPs from ISPs. Combines the speed of datacenter proxies with the legitimacy of residential IPs.
      </p>
    </header>

    <ComparisonTable proxyType="isp" />

    <section class="content">
      <h2>How to choose ISP proxies</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Stability:</strong> ISP proxies are often used for sticky sessions and long-lived identities.</li>
        <li><strong>Location:</strong> Make sure the ISP/region matches your target market.</li>
        <li><strong>Pricing model:</strong> Many ISP offerings are sold per IPâ€”compare carefully against bandwidth-based plans.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="muted">
        Try the <a href="/calculator">Price Calculator</a> for comparable $/GB pricing and see <a href="/methodology">Methodology</a> for details.
      </p>
      <p class="muted">
        Looking for a short list? See <a href="/best/isp-proxies">Best ISP Proxies</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .content ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .muted {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
